<h2 id="installation-1-minute">Installation (1 minute)</h2>
<p>If anything, Unblah is just like any other macOS app that you download and install directly from a developer (like me) instead of the App Store.</p>

<p>After youâ€™ve <a href="https://github.com/akaalias/getunblah/releases/latest/download/Unblah.dmg">downloaded the appâ€™s latest release (Unblah.dmg)</a> simply double-click the icon to open the volume.</p>

